00:38:47.232 --> 00:38:49.085
What you talking about, sugar?
It's always on you.


355
00:38:49.109 --> 00:38:50.110
Not always.

356
00:38:53.238 --> 00:38:56.116
- Thanks.
- Yeah. She went to school with my mama.


357
00:39:00.829 --> 00:39:03.248
- So you really don't drink at all?
- Huh?


358
00:39:03.957 --> 00:39:05.500
You really don't drink at all?

359
00:39:06.376 --> 00:39:07.377
I haven't tried.

360
00:39:08.003 --> 00:39:09.254
You ain't never tried a beer?

361
00:39:09.338 --> 00:39:13.050
No. Not since I've been back.
I'm kind of on a lot of medication.


362
00:39:15.844 --> 00:39:16.929
What kind of medication?

363
00:39:18.305 --> 00:39:20.891
Like, "don't-shoot-yourself-in-the-head"
