399
00:41:42.366 --> 00:41:45.369
I don't have boyfriends.
I have girlfriends.


400
00:41:46.370 --> 00:41:51.166
I mean, not right now,
but when I do, that's what I have.


401
00:41:52.626 --> 00:41:55.587
- Okay. I wasn't...
