00:43:31.850 --> 00:43:35.604
I remember… looking in my rearview mirror,

421
00:43:36.104 --> 00:43:38.523
and I could see Jess's face.

422
00:43:40.859 --> 00:43:43.111
I just remember looking in her eyes.

