00:46:06.213 --> 00:46:07.214
It's that house.

451
00:46:08.507 --> 00:46:11.051
So many nights
sitting at that kitchen table,


452
00:46:11.134 --> 00:46:12.844
and my brother would be nodding off.

453
00:46:12.928 --> 00:46:18.475
And my mom would say,
"Poor thing. He's so tired."


454
00:46:20.018 --> 00:46:21.019
I miss him.

455
00:46:24.231 --> 00:46:26.650
He and I were
both trapped in that house.

456
00:46:28.819 --> 00:46:30.571
But I'm the only
one that made it out.

457
00:46:35.117 --> 00:46:37.828
Anyway. And then I just
never thought I would come back here.


458
00:46:39.204 --> 00:46:40.664
But then I got blown up.

459
00:46:40.747 --> 00:46:42.749
You got... What? 
You got blown up?

460
00:46:43.625 --> 00:46:44.626
IED.

461
00:47:51.235 --> 00:47:52.236
Oh, shit!

